liced as per the need, â€˜Doneâ€™ button needs to be clicked which closes the split window and takes us back to the ordering screen but now with an option of selecting which check/bill we want to view shown in figure below on the right. By selecting either Check 1 or Check 2 we can settle them individually as if they were separate tables. The un-splitting of the bill can also be performed at any time by clicking on the â€˜Un-Splitâ€™ button presented above in the figure on the left. 3.2.5 Add modifications How the food is ordered by the guest might not always be the same even if the same entrÃ©e is ordered as different people prefer different way of enjoying their meals and as a hotel/restaurant guests have every right to demand things the way they prefer. Adding modifications as such means informing the kitchen regarding any special requests made by the guest so that',_binary '“NUMPY\0v\0{\'descr\': \'<f4\', \'fortran_order\': False, \'shape\': (384,), }                                                          \n¦\ç»\ãx[=\"“r½tÑ¼\ä\îÄ½/MÁ<¸=p\Ó;HMq=\Ë\Ë=¿{\Ø<!‡½•x¼^uj¼\"\ß<m=½”¯¼\Ò\ã\à¼)\Çu:˜ …=N\õ©<·ü€½\ñ;$½‚‘ü¼ß”6=\í\Ä<U\n`<N\é]¼‡¯»Œ¦½¾£:Gˆ8=\õ§=‹\ôm¼)ÿš½$\Òg½”€S¼€Ü»Û¶ß¼¡“½9\ã½0Û›½œ¸­<s\ï/½œ\åK<(i\0=?\æ;&¡==4¡¤:u0=\ÇrÀ¼*ú<\â½Â´\ó=\í?8½f)=\Ô\Ó>±:<\Âd*½ÿ¶»F\Ä4½1]œ=…\"½–\\»:pù,=Ğ‚\Ä;]¼<\õä¼:µx½-=½\rN§: “»½>o¼‰qÇ½ÿé¼- ¼QSœ<&¦\"<\ö?¡<\îv4<™¹²¼a‘=\ÈL†½†¢š;«ˆ¼	e¾¼\ì€n¼?„hº\îwi=\á?h½¡*\Ï=\n†\Ğ=	\"=jš“½¯»‚=a8µ9\ñ;k¼™¹Š¼\á\ë =^¨=ù3ƒ=Où‘=|<=\ğ»Ê¼¶‘²=\Õ^‘½ø@’=wy!½_fŠ=\î	ƒ½–İ¼gX\İ<6¸=\Õ-½{×¢½¢&~=\Ñ~È¼\è;™\\\â=ah¿¼¬H<+Kx=k¼¾Ğ½¹‚û;\å»=g,\İ<€\'!Q®½*ë®½À5ˆ<`”¼]M\Ø=P¼l£<x‘?=7A7¼\ó«t=ª]<=°ZM½¨ø@=\Ïúq;B•°½Kâ‘½\âŒË»HŠ©=?\ìV¼©=”[¼$P½\r±>7I¤=\ß\ê=,‹$=]º)}<=sª†<¥›°¼q¥·=Xú¼&£›¼\ÈC9<\ÉÙ¼—3\ö<ükq»Ÿ\"Á¼”\õU=Ä­m½ÿÊ½\':ç¼‡Œw< <útÒ½\ôK=\à[F¼73s=\ä6=p©=“\r½a‡\\¼˜™½³\è0<\ó1X½}åµ½\Ål?<kv½RoŠ¼ó¦½²’J½µ—¹½\rß‹<\÷#=9\n­½84=‡Ÿ#½R´Í¼“ø#=\0JÁ¼§\æË½Ä«==ÿ¨=\Ïâ’¼A\nÒ¼—\n=V	ºUùù¼¹a=.\à¼<.h¼\ñ¶«<!g¼\Õ2Á=c­l;H˜=\Z¿¼\Ò,ù<œ\Z<ù’–½HC<Àû>½¼7=Q©\